Re: The Penultimate Japanese IME Guide... well, almost. :)
by DavidPatrick » Sat 01.16.2010 6:35 pm I was switching between Japanese and English using Shitf + Caps Lock, which was working fine till suddenly I hit the wrong key and it started defaulting to "Full Width Alphanumeric" instead of half width. Does anyone know if there's a way to switch it back so it always reverts to half width alpha numeric after Hiragana input?
DavidPatrick
