Re: The Penultimate Japanese IME Guide... well, almost. :)
by phreadom » Mon 01.18.2010 12:59 am Some of the friendly folks in the TJP Chat offered these suggestions... (11:48:23 PM) LordOfTheFlies: If it's Windows XP it's in the language bar(11:48:40 PM) アルくん: When this happens to me, I just click the あ or Ａ in the language bar and put it back to Half-width Alphanumeric.(11:48:42 PM) LordOfTheFlies: Click the Input Option menu and choose half-width alphanumericHopefully this might help? Maybe someone else might have a better suggestion. 猿も木から落ちる
