Re: The Penultimate Japanese IME Guide... well, almost. :)
by DavidPatrick » Thu 01.21.2010 5:30 pm That's what I have to do, which takes a lot longer. I've had to set the default back to English for using the computer normally as full width alphanumeric is feck all good for the internet. It looks like there's no way to set it to default automatially. Thanks for the help.
